{"tid":223852,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"王振民：強調一國不代表國家有意放棄兩制","createTime":"2017-04-30T15:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-01T03:21:47.000Z","uid":4783,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"70ca6374e1ece20c51483efe1f0f8661c98b5556","tid":223852,"uid":4783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"【王振民：強調一國不代表國家有意放棄兩制】<br />\n【饒戈平：危及國家主權　不排除中央干預】<br />\n中聯辦法律部部長王振民指，一國不代表國家有意放棄兩制，否則香港會失去價值。<br />\n基本法委員會委員饒戈平指一旦兩制漸行漸遠，危及國家主權，不排除中央會干預。<br />\n#有線新聞 #中聯辦 #王振民 #饒戈平 #一國兩制<br />\n<br />\n呢條on9仔琴日話可能要放棄兩制，係咪俾人照完肺要改口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"791d331c99cb9f5baca46862c1ac44494fcac3e5","tid":223852,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:30:49.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"bd38ade56810cae51770915203a32d8d1866d55e","tid":223852,"uid":522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:35:32.000Z","msg":"條友都語無倫次"},{"pid":"ecb5f6f7d29c8824e60edd0306222fd597de1b83","tid":223852,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T15:38:26.000Z","msg":"吹大左即刻淆底<br />\n不過而家都無乜人理支那綠豆膠官9up<br />\n成撚日假傳聖旨"},{"pid":"cc7c1af8325d7ea75738202012ba9ffad60bf27b","tid":223852,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T17:05:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又要收返<br />\n垃圾"},{"pid":"85a6c3b21025408a461f5102f1b83093acd515a7","tid":223852,"uid":14816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:38:51.000Z","msg":"證明一國兩制無左嘅話 支那仲傷過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb58ebad0e5bfaf0db2b20b87f56354308cb5a94","tid":223852,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:47:27.000Z","msg":"講乜撚野啊 諗清楚先講啦"},{"pid":"7dfe04415a04e5d0d537f70e47031e885b2ad8fa","tid":223852,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T18:56:22.000Z","msg":"無左香港，大陸仆街啦"},{"pid":"3ce5df5517d05bfab2d338f135f75612f6d40754","tid":223852,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T21:47:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>證明一國兩制無左嘅話 支那仲傷過香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中國有千千萬萬個城市，大城市直轄市都有幾廿個，多一個香港唔多啦<br />\n但「特別」行政區俾佢走資就得兩個<br />\n用下腦都知咩事啦"},{"pid":"da92377b5e477a5b8856c40e09f069af4cab8753","tid":223852,"uid":59695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T22:09:04.000Z","msg":"又係得把死人口"},{"pid":"0aaa2ff806811731f0bc9fde485d7f3f8fe708bb","tid":223852,"uid":78769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T22:14:43.000Z","msg":"屌，戴頭盔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a29c7e062fb30d66e4767ddd356bae064f95b93","tid":223852,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-30T22:19:19.000Z","msg":"正如樓主個名"},{"pid":"37f4b5244c561f7a25ef3963593b29e002acd844","tid":223852,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:12:44.000Z","msg":"解釋即係掩飾"},{"pid":"f1512dcb59a4c5a774e66a1db81c0172a5acdeff","tid":223852,"uid":11001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:16:41.000Z","msg":"又要威 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e68d79481bc6462018a18f117ac91b068cb3b623","tid":223852,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:19:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9b759b7f68e7d518db532f4f092b55c453d8b129","tid":223852,"uid":54959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-01T03:21:28.000Z","msg":"屌你老母啦笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58936376d06de27ea48dfd2e2cfec6c3d5e6116d","tid":223852,"uid